content:
Hm?
Oh, a squirrel!{短暂停}
...Nah, not enough meat on it.

I was just chatting with Big Gem and Little Gem.{短暂停}
...What's with that confused look on your face?
Don't the gems where you're from talk to you?

Every time I stare at butterflies,
they zoom off faster.{短暂停}
It's not like I'm going to catch them.
